gnome-base/gnome-control-center:compiz - Add compiz support
gnome-base/gnome-control-center:indicator - Add appindicator support
gnome-base/gnome-session:splash - Enable gnome splash screen
gnome-extra/gnome-power-manager:indicator - Add appindicator support
gnome-extra/gnome-power-manager:policykit - Enable sys-auth/policykit authentication support
gnome-extra/polkit-gnome:indicator - Add appindicator support
gnome-extra/sensors-applet:nvidia - Enables support for sensors on NVidia chips
net-im/pidgin:bonjour - Enable bonjour (zeroconf) support
net-im/pidgin:gadu - Enable Gadu Gadu protocol support
net-im/pidgin:groupwise - Enable Novell Groupwise protocol support
net-im/pidgin:indicator - Add appindicator support
net-im/pidgin:meanwhile - Enable meanwhile support for Sametime protocol
net-im/pidgin:prediction - Enable Contact Availability Prediction plugin
net-im/pidgin:qq - Enable QQ protocol support
net-im/pidgin:silc - Enable SILC protocol support
net-im/pidgin:zephyr - Enable Zephyr protocol support
net-misc/tsclient:vnc - add basic VNC support
x11-plugins/pidgin-libnotify:indicate - Enable support for dev-libs/libindicate
x11-plugins/pidgin-libnotify:ubuntu - Enable Ubuntu style popup notification
